<bibRefCitation author="Judziewicz, E. J. &amp; Soreng, R. J. &amp; Davidse, G. &amp; Peterson, P. M. &amp; Filgueiras, T. S. &amp; Zuloaga, F. O." box="[495,755,1346,1372]" pageId="21" pageNumber="120" pagination="1 - 128" refId="ref25045" refString="Judziewicz, E. J., Soreng, R. J., Davidse, G., Peterson, P. M., Filgueiras, T. S. &amp; Zuloaga, F. O. (2000) Catalogue of New World Grasses (Poaceae): I. Subfamilies Anomochlooideae, Bambusoideae, Ehrhartoideae, and Pharoideae. Contributions from the United States National Herbarium 39: 1 - 128." type="journal article" year="2000">
